\pard\intbl\ql
{The course provides students with practical experience on specific 
projects\'2e On these projects, students apply the knowledge gained 
in previous courses\'2e\uc1\u8239?Students will be involved in projects 
and assignments in a selected company or public institution during 
the course\'2e The course thus represents a suitable bridge between 
theoretical studies and the student's future profession\'2e\uc1\u8239? 
\line
 \line
The internship is carried out in cooperation with partner companies 
or public institutions on the basis of a partnership agreement\'2e\line
}\cell\row\pard
}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
