}{\trowd\trleft0\trgaph60
\clvertalt\cellx9430
\pard\intbl\ql
{Upon successful completion of the course, students will be able to: 
\line
\_ Apply knowledge and skills gained in the course of study in performing 
work tasks \line
\_ Assess the functioning of the company's or institution's analytics 
\line
\_ Present the results of a solved work task}\cell\row\pard
