\pard\intbl\ql
{\_ Before enrolment, the student contacts the teacher who is listed 
in the internship offer and who acts as a tutor\'2e The student will 
receive a framework contract to define the fundamental rights and 
obligations of the parties (\'46IS, student, recipient organization)\'2e 
After signing it by the parties, the student is enrolled to this course\'2e 
\line
\_ After enrolment, the aims of the internship are set with the tutor 
and supervisor of the practice of the receiving organization\'2e \line
\_ The internship is supervised by a supervisor and tutor\'2e \line
\_ \'46inally, the student will prepare a report on the progress and 
results of the internship, which includes the student's assessment 
of the practice of the receiving organization\'2e \line
\_ Grading is awarded by tutor based on internship assessment, a written 
report and a practice debate\'2e \line
 }\cell\row\pard
